Package: getMODIS
Type: Package
Title: Creating and updating a local user-defined subset of the global MODIS grid data online archive. Plus pre-processing functionalities for MODIS grid data.  
Version: 0.1
Date: 2011-08-10
Depends: RCurl
Suggests: audio
Author: Matteo Mattiuzzi; Institute of Surveying, Remote Sensing and Land Information (IVFL), BOKU Vienna
Maintainer: Matteo Mattiuzzi <matteo@mattiuzzi.com>
Description: Functions for selective mirroring of the global MODIS-ftp data pool ('ftp://e4ftl01u.ecs.nasa.gov/'). Simple parameters are defining: MODIS-PRODUCT, COLLECTION, AREA and PERIOD. The functions are performing the following tasks: if not existing it creates a local archive structure equivalent to the online storage (or a simplified structure), checks if files are already stored locally, if not download the needed file(s). (Further processing routines will be added soon)
URL: http://getmodis.r-forge.r-project.org/
License: GPL (>=3)
LazyLoad: yes
